{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_01_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央 3話 莉央のプライド",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まさかLizNoirが星見市に来るなんてな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t believe LizNoir is coming to Hoshimi City!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "地方にも優しい莉央たんマジ女神！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio is a goddess! She even looks after her fans in the countryside!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ホント楽しみですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really looking forward to it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.102164954469915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "僕は葵ちゃん命ですけど！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-chan is my everything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.168831621136585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（彼女達は今や全国区のアイドルだぞ。星見市の）\n（ライブハウスに来る意味は薄い。なんだか怖いな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Why are nationally-famous idols like them)\n(putting on a show in Hoshimi city? It’s a little disliveing…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2021649544,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6633.33333340325,
          "startTime": 21.83549828780325
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 20.9021649545
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 20.9021649545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう\nいえ、もうこんにちはかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Morning.\nOr is it past morning already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.635498287803248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、神崎さん……ライブ前にどうしたんですか？\n三枝さんなら事務所にいると思いますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Kanzaki-san… I’m surprised to see you here before your live.\nI think Saegusa-san is in the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.968831621136584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 33.96883162113659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、三枝さんは不在だったわ\nそうしたらかわりに貴方に会ったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ he’s out.\nI ran into you instead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.43549828780325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 40.702164954469914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "一つ、伝えておこうかと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s something I want to tell you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.702164954469914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "率直に言うわ\nうちの事務所――バンプロは貴方達を潰しに来てる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be frank about this.\nMy agency‚ Van Productions‚ wants to crush you guys.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2021649544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 46.202164954469914
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 51.30216495446992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "私や葵の意向ではないわ\n私達はこんな姑息な手を使わなくても勝てるもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi and I have nothing to do with this.\nThe two of us don’t feel the need to resort to underhanded measures.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.16883162113659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 57.76883162113659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、場所がどこであれ、そこにステージがあるなら\n断らないし、手も抜かないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Regardless of the circumstances‚\nas long as the stage is there‚ we won’t turn it down‚ and we won’t cut corners.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.86883162113659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 64.58932430629994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "自分達の意志じゃないって\n三枝さんに分かってほしくて、ここに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You wanted to make sure Saegusa-san knew\nthat you had nothing to do with this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.455990973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんというより\n貴方の抱えるアイドル達にね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not so much Saegusa-san\nbut more the idols you’re managing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.53065753663644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 74.06399086996977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "私達がこそこそとズルいことをしているなんて\n思われるのは心外だもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be annoying if we were seen as\npeople who resort to cloaks and daggers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.76399087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 78.88170057420993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "私達はそんなつまらないことはしない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We don’t waste our time on this nonsense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.88170057420993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（なるほど）\n（プライドの高い彼女らしいな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I see.)\n(She really does have a strong sense of pride.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.94274377311334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 85.30941043978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "わざわざありがとうございます\n彼女達には俺から言っておきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for letting me know.\nI’ll pass this on to the girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.27607710644666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "貴方やっぱり素直なのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re honest to a fault.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.88673858021417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 92.15340524688085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、星見プロが潰れる前にうちに転職したら？\nその方が貴方の将来のためだと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Why not jump ship before Hoshimi Productions goes down?\nIt would be better for your career.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8867385802142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 99.9867385802142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "ここもいつまで続くか分からないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who knows how long this agency will last?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9867385802142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すみませんが、それは出来ません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ but I can’t do that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.61379064892452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 105.31379064892448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.31379064892448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……そう答えると思ったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you would say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.11379064892452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 109.21379064892452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、なんでそんなことを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then why did you—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.21379064892452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "試させてもらったのよ\n担当アイドルを捨てるような男だったらいらないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was testing you.\nI have no use for someone who would abandon the idols he manages.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.23517393444698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 118.00184060111364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "貴方は三枝さんとは違うようね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re different from Saegusa-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.00184060111364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
